# Object Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000417> (achieves_planned_objective)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000111> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000417> "achieves_planned_objective")
