# Object Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000080> (quality of)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000111> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000080> "quality of"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000080> "this red color is a quality of this apple"@en)
