AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000098> "2009-03-16: provenance: term imported from OBI_0000187, which had original definition \"A data format specification is a plan which organizes
