AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000144> "2009/09/28 Alan Ruttenberg. Fucoidan-use-case"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000144> "2009/10/23 Alan Ruttenberg: We need to work on the definition still"@en)
