AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000412> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000184> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/iao.owl>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000412> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000184> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/obi.owl>)
