AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000232> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000017> "govt agents responsible for creating regulations; proxies for enforcing regulations.  CDISC definition:  regulatory authorities. Bodies having the power to regulate. NOTE: In the ICH GCP guideline the term includes the authorities that review submitted clinical data and those that conduct inspections. These bodies are sometimes referred to as competent"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000017> "regulatory role"@en)
