# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000069> (number of degrees of freedom)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000069> "The number degree of freedom is a count evaluating the number of values in a calculation that can vary. In statistics, the number of degrees of freedom ν is equal to N-1 in the case of the direct measurement of a quantity estimated by the arithmetic mean of N independent observations."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000116> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000069> "AGB: Addressing issue https://github.com/ISA-tools/stato/issues/77, removed 'number of degrees of freedom' subClassOf 'count' and added 'number of degrees of freedom' subClassOf 'measurement datum' instead.

For more details, see https://stats.stackexchange.com/questions/116511/explanation-for-non-integer-degrees-of-freedom-in-t-test-with-unequal-variances"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000069> "Alejandra Gonzalez-Beltran"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000069> "Hanna Ćwiek")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000069> "Orlaith Burke")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000069> "Philippe Rocca-Serra"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000069> "http://stats.stackexchange.com/questions/16921/how-to-understand-degrees-of-freedom"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000069> "http://www.optique-ingenieur.org/en/courses/OPI_ang_M07_C01/co/Contenu_07.html"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000069> "the rank of the quadratic form (mathematical definition)"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000069> "number of degrees of freedom"@en)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000069> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000047>)

