# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000266> (Bayes factor)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000266> "Bayes factor is a ratio between 2 probabilities of observing data according 2 distinct models. It is used in Bayes model selection to evaluate which model best explains the data. if K<0, the model used in the denominator term is supported, if K>1, the model used in the numerator term is supported.
The Bayes factor is about the plausibility of 2 different models"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000266> "Alejandra Gonzalez-Beltran"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000266> "Orlaith Burke")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000266> "Philippe Rocca-Serra"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000266> "adapted from Wikipedia
last accessed 2013-11-13"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000266> "Bayes factor"@en)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000266> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000184>)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000266> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000136> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000107>))
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000266> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000295> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000143>))

# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000288> (absence of difference hypothesis)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000288> "A null hypothesis which states that no difference exists between 2 or more groups being considered."@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000288> "Alejandra Gonzalez-Beltran"@en)
