AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000119> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000566> "adapted from:
http://mathworld.wolfram.com/Eigenvalue.html

last accessed: 04/07/2018"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000566> "eigen value"@en)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000566> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000027>)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/STATO_0000566> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000648>)
